PN,41401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1783667970
OL,3,CMother and baby homes admissions in NI
OL,4,C2,000 higher than first estimated
OL,6,FThe estimated number of women admitted
OL,7,Fto mother and baby homes and Magdalene
OL,8,FLaundries in Northern Ireland is some
OL,9,F2,000 higher than previously thought,
OL,10,Fa report has found.
OL,12,FThe co-chairmen of the Truth Recovery
OL,13,FIndependent Panel found that "human
OL,14,Frights abuses, degrading treatment,
OL,15,Fand forced separation of families are
OL,16,Frecurring and frequent" in evidence
OL,17,Ffrom survivors of the homes.
OL,26,@uD@^OUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
