FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1783667970
OL,3,CMother and baby homes admissions in NI
OL,4,C2,000 higher than first estimated
OL,6,FThe 10-person Independent Panel, which
OL,7,Fincludes three victims/ survivors, was
OL,8,Fappointed in 2023 by the Executive
OL,9,FOffice to look into the workings of
OL,10,Fthe institutions that were run by the
OL,11,FCatholic Church, religious orders,
OL,12,Fsome Protestant denominations, and the
OL,13,FState, until the 1990s.
OL,15,FLast week Stormont passed a Bill for a
OL,16,Fpublic inquiry and financial redress
OL,17,Fscheme relating to mother and baby
OL,18,Finstitutions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1783667970
OL,3,CMother and baby homes admissions in NI
OL,4,C2,000 higher than first estimated
OL,6,FOn Tuesday the Panel published their
OL,7,Ffinal report, describing it as "the
OL,8,Flargest and most comprehensive
OL,9,Fcollection of lived-experience
OL,10,Ftestimony in Northern Ireland in
OL,11,Fconnection to these institutions".
OL,13,FRevised figures in the report show
OL,14,Fadmissions to mother and baby
OL,15,Finstitutions had increased from the
OL,16,Fpreviously estimated 10,500 to 12,062,
OL,17,Fand admissions to Magdalene Laundries
OL,18,Fand related institutions had risen
OL,19,Ffrom 3,455 to 3,753 after access to
OL,20,Fadditional records.
OL,26,@oD@`OUsD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1783667970
OL,3,CMother and baby homes admissions in NI
OL,4,C2,000 higher than first estimated
OL,6,FMagdalene Laundries refers to three St
OL,7,FMary's Homes, which were operated by
OL,8,Fthe Good Shepherd Sisters and
OL,9,FThorndale Industrial Home, which was
OL,10,Foperated by the Salvation Army.
OL,12,FThe Panel's final report draws from
OL,13,Fthe evidence of almost 300 victims and
OL,14,Fsurvivors, their relatives and others
OL,15,Fwith experience of the institutions.
OL,17,FThe Panel identified a series of
OL,18,Fserious human rights issues that they
OL,19,Fsay will require further investigation
OL,20,Fby the forthcoming public inquiry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1783667970
OL,3,CMother and baby homes admissions in NI
OL,4,C2,000 higher than first estimated
OL,6,FA theme emerging from evidence of
OL,7,Fsurvivors was the sexual abuse of some
OL,8,Fgirls and women before their
OL,9,Fadmission; and of abuse, neglect and
OL,10,Finadequate care in the mother and baby
OL,11,Finstitutions.
OL,13,FThe report highlights that their
OL,14,Fexperiences amounted to degrading
OL,15,Ftreatment and, in some cases, are
OL,16,Flikely to reach the threshold of
OL,17,Finhuman treatment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1783667970
OL,3,CMother and baby homes admissions in NI
OL,4,C2,000 higher than first estimated
OL,6,FThe report makes 70 recommendations,
OL,7,Fincluding 28 to the forthcoming public
OL,8,Finquiry and 39 to the Northern Ireland
OL,9,FExecutive.
OL,11,FRecommendations for the Stormont
OL,12,FExecutive include the immediate
OL,13,Fappointment of the chairman of the
OL,14,Fpublic inquiry, highlighting that
OL,15,F"synergies that should have been
OL,16,Fcreated between the Panel and the
OL,17,Finquiry have been lost due to delay in
OL,18,Festablishing the public inquiry".
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1783667970
OL,3,CMother and baby homes admissions in NI
OL,4,C2,000 higher than first estimated
OL,6,FThe Panel also advises that women and
OL,7,Fgirls who gave birth in workhouses and
OL,8,Fwere separated from their children,
OL,9,Fand the children who were separated
OL,10,Ffrom their mothers, should be included
OL,11,Fin the scope of the payment scheme.
OL,13,FThe Independent Panel co-chairmen,
OL,14,FProfessors Leanne McCormick and Sean
OL,15,FO'Connell said the report marks "a
OL,16,Fsignificant milestone in the pursuit
OL,17,Fof truth and justice for victims/
OL,18,Fsurvivors who spent time in these
OL,19,Finstitutions".
OL,26,@wD@aOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1783667970
OL,3,CMother and baby homes admissions in NI
OL,4,C2,000 higher than first estimated
OL,6,F"They have been fundamental to our
OL,7,Funderstanding of what took place in
OL,8,Fthe institutions and the enduring
OL,9,Fimpacts, enabling us to offer our
OL,10,Fanalysis, revealing the hidden history
OL,11,Fof the institutions and the associated
OL,12,Fpathways and practices," they said.
OL,14,F"The Panel's report includes testimony
OL,15,Ffrom almost 300 people who were
OL,16,Fdirectly affected by the institutions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@XO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1783667970
OL,3,CMother and baby homes admissions in NI
OL,4,C2,000 higher than first estimated
OL,6,F"We hope this, alongside our work with
OL,7,FPRONI (Public Record Office of
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland) to preserve
OL,9,Fthousands of records for the first
OL,10,Ftime, will help ensure that the work
OL,11,Fof the public inquiry can be carried
OL,12,Fout as swiftly as possible and that
OL,13,Fthe goals of truth, acknowledgment and
OL,14,Faccountability are reached.
OL,16,F"We have greatly advanced our
OL,17,Funderstanding of the issues and now
OL,18,Fhave much more detail about how these
OL,19,Finstitutions were run in Northern
OL,20,FIreland.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1783667970
OL,3,CMother and baby homes admissions in NI
OL,4,C2,000 higher than first estimated
OL,6,F"Issues of gender-based
OL,7,Fdiscrimination, human rights abuses,
OL,8,Fdegrading treatment, and forced
OL,9,Fseparation of families are recurring
OL,10,Fand frequent. They should all be
OL,11,Fexamined thoroughly by the public
OL,12,Finquiry.
OL,14,F"We have presented our report to
OL,15,Fvictims/survivors and we have shared
OL,16,Fit with the First and deputy First
OL,17,FMinisters.
OL,19,F"It is now for the Executive and a
OL,20,Fpublic inquiry to take this forward.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1783667970
OL,3,CMother and baby homes admissions in NI
OL,4,C2,000 higher than first estimated
OL,6,F"Though a chairperson has not yet been
OL,7,Fappointed for the public inquiry, the
OL,8,FIndependent Panel remains willing to
OL,9,Fmeet and engage with them once they
OL,10,Fare appointed, to assist the inquiry's
OL,11,Fwork."
